        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for GdeS’s <hi rend="italic">Le monde des plantes</hi> [1879].</p>  
<p>CD has just read "Végétation polaire" [<hi rend="italic">C. R. Congr. Int. Sci. Geogr.</hi> 1 (1878): 197–242] with interest. Hooker gave it conspicuous place in his Royal Society Address (1878).</p> 
        </abstract>
